  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1723165318\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1723165318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1723165318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >😸 A portion of the profit from this game will be allocated to street cat rescue and support initiatives. 😻</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/63e0d64bc2422e2bd45ba3ac15e5a4b5.avif?t=1723165318\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meowsterpiece Museum is a hidden object game where you need to find cats in famous paintings. Each painting has 50 cats to be found. </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/860104010deb5cc3e434c0167c905d01.poster.avif?t=1723165318\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/860104010deb5cc3e434c0167c905d01.webm?t=1723165318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/860104010deb5cc3e434c0167c905d01.mp4?t=1723165318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete a level and download the wallpaper of the painting.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/fe49cf5fdf3f810a68260ff2d836c20b.poster.avif?t=1723165318\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2807600/extras/fe49cf5fdf3f810a68260ff2d836c20b.webm?t=1723165318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Confirmed Paintings:</h2><br>🖼️ The Starry Night - Vincent Van Gato<br>🖼️ The Last Supper - Leonardo da Vinkitty<br>🖼️ The Persistence of Memory - Salvador Pawli<br>🖼️ Three Musicians - Pablo Picatso<br>🖼️ The Farm - Joan Meowró<br>🖼️ The Three Life - Gustav Clawmt<br>🖼️ Dance at Moulin de la Galette - Purrerre Auguste Renoir<br>🖼️ The Papaya Tree - Tarsila do Amiau<br>🖼️ A Sunday Afternoon on the Island of La Grande Jatte - Georges Siamat<br>🖼️ The Afternoon Meal - Claude Meownet<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>​🎵​ Original soundtrack.<br>🎨 10 famous paintings.<br>🐈 500 cats to find.<br>🖥️​ Wallpapers of paintings to download.<br>🧩 Game experience designed for both think and relax.",
